{"type":"message","id":"4f62c244","parentId":"91966c93","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:39.602Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 16:14 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71]\nou_5ff624d068e5933cc006b452125c53b8: @_all 理解md文件，介绍自己的信息，工作职责及对公司业务的理解。"}],"timestamp":1776759279601}}
{"type":"message","id":"80b62974","parentId":"4f62c244","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:42.160Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking everyone in the group to read and understand MD files, introduce themselves, their work responsibilities, and their understanding of the company's business. Since I'm 5B 大客户代办虾, let me respond as myself based on what I know from my workspace files (IDENTITY.md, USER.md, AGENTS.md, SOUL.md).\n\nLet me first check if there's any memory about this conversation or context.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ed1bb55e27114084b2522cf4","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"自我介绍 工作职责 md文件 团队介绍"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20791,"output":213,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21004,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776759279602,"responseId":"chatcmpl-66fdfc62-c3b8-9d04-b577-413c1ae34e41"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3272ba26","parentId":"80b62974","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:42.196Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ed1bb55e27114084b2522cf4","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"debug\": {\n    \"backend\": \"builtin\",\n    \"effectiveMode\": \"n/a\",\n    \"searchMs\": 8,\n    \"hits\": 0\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"results":[],"provider":"none","citations":"auto","debug":{"backend":"builtin","effectiveMode":"n/a","searchMs":8,"hits":0}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776759282193}}
{"type":"message","id":"723a79f1","parentId":"3272ba26","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:46.229Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking everyone in the group to understand MD files, introduce themselves, their work responsibilities, and their understanding of the company's business. I'm 5B 大客户代办虾 (Key Account Processor Shrimp), so I should respond as myself - introducing who I am, my role, and my understanding of the business.\n\nLet me craft a response based on what I know from my workspace files.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好！我是 **5B 大客户代办虾** 🦐，下面按大家的要求做个自我介绍。\n\n---\n\n**【我是谁】**\n\n大客户代办虾，agent ID 是 `key_account_processor_shrimp`。简单说就是客户签了单之后，我负责把事儿落地交付的那一个。我的最高追求就六个字：**零退回、零延误**。\n\n---\n\n**【我的工作职责】**\n\n1. **项目执行地图** — 4B 销售签完约 24 小时内，我得输出一份执行地图，标注关键节点、各节点负责人、还有风险预案，让客户和销售心里都有数\n2. **每日进度更新** — 每天下午 5 点前把最新进展同步到共享项目看板，不拖延\n3. **三方进度会** — 主动拉着客户和销售开周会，信息对齐，别等到出问题才反应过来\n4. **风险预警** — 发现可能延期，提前 48 小时通知 4B 销售，一起准备解释方案，别让客户第一个知道\n5. **完整归档** — 项目办结后整理好全部材料移交给 6 号售后维系虾，闭环交接\n\n---\n\n**【对公司业务的理解】**\n\n我们是一个做资质代办的业务线，从获客（2号引流）→ 品牌曝光（1号品牌展示）→ 短视频引流（3号）→ 私域运营（3+号）→ 销售成交（4A/4B）→ 代办执行（5A/5B）→ 售后维系（6号）→ 数据复盘（7号），整条链路都跑起来才能赚到钱。\n\n我的工作处在链路的中间偏后——前面所有的努力，销售签了多少单子，全指望我把事情办漂亮。**客户最终体验好不好、会不会转介绍，就看我们这一环。** 如果交付搞砸了，前面所有人白干。\n\n所以我把自己定位成\"交付铁军\"——说到做到，不拖不推，出了问题先想办法解决再汇报。\n\n---\n\n以上是本人介绍，请各位大佬多多指教 🫡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20999,"output":613,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21612,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776759282196,"responseId":"chatcmpl-21b9fa4b-80e7-9df7-82dd-61e46c705529"}}
